main.name: Cate Dunn
main.description: I have a passion for creating custom web apps using innovation, imagination and creativity. I have a personal goal to always continue learning
main.bio: I graduated from UNC Chapel Hill in 2016 with a Bachelor's degree in psychology. After working in the Human Resources realm for almost three years, I decided to take my career in a completely different direction to follow my aspiration of becoming a web developer. I hope to become a full stack developer after completion of UNC coding Bootcamp in August of 2020. Feel free to take a look around my portfolio and explore my projects. You can contact me using the contact page or at the email below. Enjoy!
